WEBVTT

1
00:22:32.050 --> 00:22:33.390
What a pity.

2
00:32:16.680 --> 00:32:19.220
Papa has to go to work. my dear.

3
00:33:01.640 --> 00:33:02.770
Who wants to kill you?

4
00:33:05.520 --> 00:33:08.900
A single insect may bring down
an entire country.

5
00:33:09.020 --> 00:33:11.150
Which insect wants to kill you today?

6
00:33:11.280 --> 00:33:13.240
I don't know. but I intend to find out.

7
00:35:15.150 --> 00:35:16.860
-Is this my speech?
-Yes.

8
00:35:25.740 --> 00:35:29.750
-Is the lighting okay?
-The lighting is perfect. jefe.

9
00:35:30.370 --> 00:35:31.670
Thank you. General.

10
00:35:37.170 --> 00:35:39.010
You phone is ringing. el jefe.

11
00:35:44.760 --> 00:35:47.850
-Hello?
-Jorge. my nephew!

12
00:35:48.390 --> 00:35:49.350
Uncle?

13
00:35:50.230 --> 00:35:51.400
Correct.

14
00:35:52.400 --> 00:35:55.730
I'm out here walking through the jungle.
How are you?

15
00:35:56.440 --> 00:35:57.530
All good?

16
00:36:00.780 --> 00:36:03.370
-How are you. uncle?
-I'm fantastic.

17
00:36:03.490 --> 00:36:07.040
I'm walking through the jungle
with an absolutely lovely woman.

18
00:36:07.240 --> 00:36:11.160
-The gringo journalist?
-Yes. the beautiful Claire Wellington.

19
00:36:57.750 --> 00:37:00.090
Yes. yes. don't worry. See you soon.

20
00:37:01.590 --> 00:37:04.300
We...we were all worried for you.

21
00:37:04.430 --> 00:37:06.970
Sure. Great. God bless you!

22
00:37:11.220 --> 00:37:12.850
My uncle isn't dead.

23
00:37:15.850 --> 00:37:18.190
Our partners will not be pleased.

24
00:48:52.590 --> 00:48:54.260
Thank you for your help.

25
00:48:56.510 --> 00:48:58.100
You're welcome. Mr. Pettits.

26
00:54:08.530 --> 00:54:10.240
You're more beautiful than on TV.

27
00:54:13.540 --> 00:54:15.790
The hulk here. he scares me.

28
00:57:43.960 --> 00:57:47.130
My promise and my legacy

29
00:57:47.250 --> 00:57:51.010
is that wealth from these metals will
be invested solely and exclusively

30
00:57:51.340 --> 00:57:54.050
to enrich the people of Paldonia.

31
00:57:54.590 --> 00:57:55.510
Long live Paldonia!

32
01:09:01.260 --> 01:09:03.930
I said. where is President Venegas?

33
01:09:08.520 --> 01:09:11.140
Where is President Venegas?

34
01:09:26.780 --> 01:09:29.200
-This is your car?
-Yes. Mister.

35
01:19:47.030 --> 01:19:48.820
-You're alive. Papi?
-I am.

36
01:19:49.280 --> 01:19:52.200
It's good to see you.
It was not my men who attacked you.

37
01:19:52.330 --> 01:19:55.620
-I know. I know. Espresso?
-Naturally.

38
01:19:57.370 --> 01:19:58.460
Who is this?

39
01:26:25.090 --> 01:26:26.300
Uncle!

40
01:26:29.810 --> 01:26:31.270
I am not here to hurt you.

41
01:28:09.240 --> 01:28:11.570
You're okay. you're okay. You're okay.

42
01:28:15.700 --> 01:28:16.910
Uncle...

43
01:28:17.620 --> 01:28:20.670
Uncle...uncle.

44
01:28:22.670 --> 01:28:25.000
They killed...me.

45
01:28:28.130 --> 01:28:30.050
I'm... I'm sorry.

46
01:29:01.290 --> 01:29:02.330
Surrender!

47
01:29:07.000 --> 01:29:08.210
Surrender!

48
01:29:09.420 --> 01:29:13.760
Soldiers! I know you are obeying orders.

49
01:29:15.050 --> 01:29:19.060
My children.
you don't have to do this.

50
01:29:20.520 --> 01:29:26.060
My brothers. you can change
the destiny of this country.

51
01:29:26.360 --> 01:29:27.650
Not for me.

52
01:29:29.230 --> 01:29:30.570
But for you.

53
01:29:32.740 --> 01:29:34.200
For your mothers.

54
01:29:35.120 --> 01:29:36.530
For you fathers.

55
01:29:37.950 --> 01:29:39.620
For your children.

56
01:29:40.700 --> 01:29:43.120
This country has bled for too long.

57
01:29:43.580 --> 01:29:45.830
This madness has to end.

58
01:29:53.300 --> 01:29:55.090
Now is the time to fight.

59
01:29:55.510 --> 01:29:58.930
Fight for this land.

60
01:30:03.690 --> 01:30:07.980
My brothers. defend your homeland.

61
01:32:36.550 --> 01:32:38.090
Mr. Venegas?

62
01:32:40.720 --> 01:32:42.300
Mr. President?

63
01:32:43.300 --> 01:32:44.510
Yes...

64
01:37:41.100 --> 01:37:44.060
Nice to meet you - I think.
